B.	ONE DEVELOPMENT VISTA (MHAGC- MENTAL HEALTH FOCUS) WILL STRENGTHEN THE ORGANIZATION'S DEVELOPMENT PLAN FOCUSED ON SUPPORTING THE SUSTAINABILITY AND EXPANSION OF EXISTING PROGRAMS; 
