D.	ONE PROGRAM & SYSTEM ASSESSMENT VISTA (MHAGC- MENTAL HEALTH FOCUS) WILL BUILD ORGANIZATIONAL CAPACITY BY ASSESSING AND DOCUMENTING CURRENT AGENCY OPERATIONS SYSTEMS AND WORKING WITH LEADERSHIP TO IMPLEMENT RECOMMENDATIONS TO MAKE OPERATIONS MORE EFFICIENT; THIS INDIVIDUAL WILL DOCUMENT OUTCOMES OF CURRENT AGENCY PROGRAMMING IN ORDER TO ENHANCE OUTREACH, DEVELOPMENT AND VOLUNTEER RECRUITMENT PROCCESSES; 
